Package com.adobe.idp.dsc.registry.infomodel

Interface Summary
Component This interface provides support for managing components.
CompositeEditorAttribute A CompositeEditorAttribute is an attribute contained in a composite editor.
CompositeEditorComponent This class is the transfer object used to retrieve and store configuration information related to composite editor components used in PropertyEditor objects.
CompositeEditorObject A CompositeEditorObject object is an attribute contained in a composite editor component.
CompositeEditorSimpleAttribute A CompositeEditorSimpleAttribute object is an attribute contained in a composite editor.
ConfigParameter A ConfigParameter object stores information about configuration values.
Connector A Connector object allows you to retrieve information about supported connectors.
DataType Data type.
Endpoint An Endpoint object enables you to set and retrieve endpoint information.
EndpointCategory An EndpointCategory object enables you to retrieve information about the endpoint category.
EndpointURI An EndpointURI object enables you to retrieve information about the endpoint URI.
Fault A Fault object stores the metadata related to faults for a service.
InputParameter An InputParameter object contains the data expected as input for a service.
InputParameterMapping Defines the input data mapping, including data type values, that an endpoint supports.
Operation An Operation object contains metadata describing a service operation.
OutputParameter An OutputParameter object contains metadata describing the output parameters expected for an operation that belongs to a service.
Parameter /** A Parameter object contains metadata describing the parameters expected for an operation.
PermissionGrant A PermissionGrant object contains a permission for a service.
PropertyEditor Provides a reference between various parameters (configuration, input, or output) used by a service for a PropertyEditorComponent that the parameters explicitly reference.
PropertyEditorComponent A PropertyEditorComponent object provides access to the metadata and content contained within a physical property editor component file.
Service An Service object allows you to retrieve information about the service.
ServiceCategory A ServiceCategory object allows you to retrieve information about the service category.
ServiceConfiguration A ServiceConfiguration object provides access to metadata describing the document service.
